headline.print_headline: Improved Swiss Confident of Last-16 Berth-Hitzfeld
headline.main: Improved Swiss Confident of Last-16 Berth-Hitzfeld

lead_paragraph: Switzerland have improved since the last World Cup in 2010 and are confident they can reach the last 16 as one of two qualifiers from Group E, coach Ottmar Hitzfeld said on Saturday.
